# Github App

This is an app to add tags to starred git repositories.

# Group Repositories

## Repositories Collection [/api/repositories]

### Get all starred repositories according to username [GET /api/repositories/{username}/starred]
+ Parameter
  + username: "tiagodavi" (string) - Username on Github

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  + Body
      [
        {
          "repository": {
            "description": "A MVC framework with Node.js + Express.js",
            "git_repo_id": 21737112,
            "id": 598,
            "language": "JavaScript",
            "name": "baconpress",
            "url": "https://github.com/danilodeveloper/baconpress.git",
            "tags": [
              {
                "tag": {
                  "name": "repo",
                  "id": 1,
                  "repository_id": 1
                }
              }
            ],
            "tag_recommendations": [
              "baconpress",
              "php",
              "angular",
              "backend",
              "frontend",
              "vue"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]

