# Group Tags

## Tags Collection [/api/tags]

### Update tag [PUT /api/tags/{id}]
+ Parameter
    + id: 1 (number) - Tag ID
    
+ Request
    {
      "tag": {
        "name": "new-name"
      }
    }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body
        {
          "tag": {
            "id": 161,
            "name": "new-name",
            "repository_id": 593
          }
        }

### Delete tag [DELETE /api/tags/{id}]
+ Parameter
    + id: 1 (number) - Tag ID

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body
        {
          "tag": {
            "id": 161,
            "name": "new-name",
            "repository_id": 593
          }
        }
